text: Alle bhai.. tere ko firs year me pareshan karne me bahut mje aaye the(Sachan ko blame karte hai apne jhagdo ke liye, whi catalyst tha). Pr saath me dusre wing ko gaaliyan dene me bhi mje aaye. Pure 4 saal apun ne kyi baar jhagde kiye phir milaap kiya.. Thanks bhai... Amazing+Unique aadmi hai tu.
author: Pratyush Mani Manav

text: Aur mishra ji, bahut mast aadmi hai aap. First year me gaali nhi dene se final year me kuchh selected gaaliya dene ltak dekha hai aapko. Apun kyi baar kisi baat ko lekar ek dusre se kuchh na kuchh ladte rhe(Aapse ladne me bhi mja hi aata tha, ek baar jyada hi ho gya tha sorry uske liye). Pr overall aap bahut mast aadmi rhe. Aapki gpl bhi hui hai kyi baar(mere baad sabse jyada aapki hi hui hogi). Vaise to aap sweet aadmi hai pr nashe me aap bahut hi achchhe hote hai. Love you bhai‚ù§Ô∏è.‚ù§Ô∏è..
author: Pratyush Mani Manav

text: Aur bhaiii..., 4 saal beet gye. First year me saath rhe aur bahut jhagde kiye(maybe campus me sabse jyade). Kapurwan ko light jlakar sone na dena(mje aate the). Apun ne bhi jhagde kiye, ek me dono ne limit cross kr di(Pr usko ek memorable moment maan lete hai, aisa thode hai ki hr din koi tatte pakadta hai). Tere aur arya ke bate sunne me alag hi mja tha... Love you Bhai..
author: Pratyush Mani Manav

text: Aur bhai.. apun same class me the resonance me, isi se apni baat start hui first year me(Now i wish, reonance me bhi apni baat hui hoti.) Tera sense of humour, sabse mast cheej hai. Har ek baat ke liye response hota hai tere pass. Apun ne 4 saal bahut bakchodiya ki, Dusre wing waalo ko gaaliyan dene me alag hi josh tha. Love you bro... Aur dekhte hai kb milte hai...
author: Pratyush Mani Manav

text: Ram Ram Bhai.. Apun ki jan pahchan to mishra ke mje lete lete hui. Cycle maangne se lekar koi bhi kaam ho bhai tu man nhi krta tha‚ù§. Aadmi bahut achchha hai bhai tu. Phir milenge aage khi na khi..
author: Pratyush Mani Manav

text: Aur bhai, tu hi hai jisne mere ko football khelna start karwaya. Hamesha Shopc ho ya gate ke bahar jana ho ya library/ncl sab jagah agar puchho to saath jane e liye taiyaar rahte the. Ek bar summer me tune gate tak aaya tha chhodne ke liye cycle pr. Logo ke mje dusro se liwana. Asli saanp hai bhai(compliment hai‚ù§Ô∏è‚ù§Ô∏è). 69 ki meaning tere through hi pta chali mereko(Ab maan liya 96 mere hi the). Bahut hi kam log hai jinhe mai bol sakta hu ki mai friends tha, aur bhai tu ek sabse achchha dost rha hai. Fir milenge dekhte hai banglore me. Love you dost ‚ù§Ô∏è.‚ù§Ô∏è.‚ù§Ô∏è..

text: Aur Bhai! pahli bar ek dusre se first year class me achhe se mile. Phir tbse saath me sabhi class me baithne aur sone ka mja hi alag tha. Aur Apne room me raat ko TA bnana aur kapurwan ko pareshan krna light jlakar. VAise normally jyade bachcho ko janta nhi tha mai, mostly logo ko tere through jana. 2 saal saath me roomie rahe vah apne mje the. Saath me gate pr momos khane jana mast tha yr(momos treat ke liye kabhi bhi bol sakta hai hamesha taiyaar rahunga). Love you roomieüòçüòçüòç
